# SSL Certificates Directory
# Place your SSL certificate files here for HTTPS support:
#   - certs/server.crt   (SSL certificate)
#   - certs/server.key    (SSL private key)
# For production, use Let's Encrypt or your CA's certificates.
# Without these files, nginx will fail to start with SSL enabled.
# To disable SSL, comment out the 443 listener in nginx.conf.
